mods.abstract: Three color window card (red and black on split fountain, yellow to blue) Hatch poster announcing the Duke of Paducah show featuring the George Morgan, Anita Carter, Annie Lou, Danny Dill, Lew Childre and the Candy Kids at the Livestock Auditorium on November 16. Poster features metal photoplates of the Duke of Paducah, George Morgan, Anita Carter, Annie Lou, Danny Dill, and Lew Childre.
